hackathon-description-text: At se² we work hard to deliver valuable services to our customers, clients, and one another.

hackathon-judges.judge-role: Senior Vice President, Strategy and Corporate Planning

hackathon-eligibility:
Individuals must be employed by se²
Must be assembled prior to the day of the hackathon and consist of 2-5 people
hackathon-rules:
1. You must be employed by se² to participate
2. Have fun!
3. Teams are 2-5 people
4. Only use the tools provided  (event issued laptop and list of approved applications)
5. All projects including code and presentation must be submitted by 12:30 PM CST on Sunday, June 5.
5. Each team has 8 min maximum to present their project to the judges
6. Wear your se2 badge at all times during the event for security purposes

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Each member of the 1st place team will receive their choice of an Apple iPad Air 2 or Samsung Tab S2.
hackathon-prizes.prize-title: 1st Place - Apple iPad Air 2 or Samsung Tab S2

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Each member of the 2nd place team will receive their choice of an Apple Watch Sport or Samsung Gear S2.
hackathon-prizes.prize-title: 2nd Place - Apple Watch Sport or Samsung Gear S2

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: Each member of the 3rd place team will receive a CreoPop 3D Pen.

hackathon-location-google-maps: https://maps.google.com/?q=1 SW Security Benefit Pl, Topeka, KS 66606, USA

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: You must submit your presentation on the devpost site by the deadline, present your idea and demo within the 8 minute timeframe, and all portions of the presentation must be complete.
